        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%d weken"
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "e.g. '4 weeks'"
    },
    "Consistency rewards regularity. Half comes from how often you run this week, the other half from how many weeks in a row you keep it up.": {
      "localizations": {
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Consistentie beloont regelmaat. De helft komt uit hoe vaak je déze week loopt, de andere helft uit hoeveel weken op rij je dat volhoudt."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Consistency description"
    },
    "Runs this week (max 40)": {
      "localizations": {
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Runs deze week (max 40)"
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Score breakdown section title"
    },
    "Streak (max 60)": {
      "localizations": {
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Streak (max 60)"
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Score breakdown section title"
    },
    "Running 3 or more times a week gives the maximum weekly points.": {
      "localizations": {
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "3 of meer keer per week lopen geeft het maximale week-punten."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Consistency tip"
    },
    "Every consecutive week builds your streak further — at 12 weeks in a row you're at the maximum.": {
      "localizations": {
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Elke opeenvolgende week bouwt je streak verder op — bij 12 weken op rij zit je op het maximum."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Consistency tip"
    },
    "This week only counts once you hit it, but it doesn't break your streak while it's still ongoing — only a missed, completed week does that.": {
      "localizations": {
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Deze week telt pas mee zodra je 'm haalt, maar breekt je streak niet zolang hij nog loopt — pas een gemiste, afgeronde week doet dat."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Consistency tip"
    },
